{{engname|《到爱的距离》|The Distance of Love}} ，改编自同名网络小说，剧本创作由小说原作者编剧朱朱亲自执笔完成<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2013-10-14/10264023324.shtml |title=《到爱》东方开播 医疗行业剧传递正能量 |date=2013-10-14 |publisher=新浪娱乐 |work= |language=zh-cn |accessdate=2013-10-14 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608213556/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2013-10-14/10264023324.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是一部以[[医院|医院]]背景為题材的情感[[电视剧|电视剧]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ent.kankanews.com/news/2013-09-16/2738283.shtml |title=《到爱的距离》李晨张馨予演情侣曝片花  |accessdate=2013-09-29 |archive-date=2013-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002010508/http://ent.kankanews.com/news/2013-09-16/2738283.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由简川訸导演、[[李晨_(演员)|李晨]]监制并主演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2013-10-10/15374021283.shtml |title=《到爱》将播 发布会张馨予缺席李晨黑脸 |date=2013-10-10 |publisher=新浪娱乐 |work= |language=zh-cn |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608091806/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2013-10-10/15374021283.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於2013年7月[[杀青|杀青]]，於同年10月8日在山东电视影视频道首播<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iqilu.com/html/yingshi/news/2013/0930/1685802.shtml |title=《到爱的距离》李晨张馨予首次出演情侣 |date=2013-09-30 |publisher=齐鲁网 |work= |language=zh-cn |accessdate=2013-10-04 |archive-date=2019-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602180919/http://www.iqilu.com/html/yingshi/news/2013/0930/1685802.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於10月14日在[[东方卫视|东方卫视]]上映。

